<F P=105>  Polish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] At a press conference in the Sejm, Jozef Oleksy 
[Sejm speaker] and Marek Borowski [deputy leader of the 
Democratic Left Alliance] have announced that Dariusz Rosati 
remains the only coalition candidate for the posts of deputy 
prime minister and finance minister. 
  They also said that the media had distorted yesterday's 
statement by Leszek Miller [labor and social policy minister], 
reporting that there was already a new candidate. They 
explained that Leszek Miller had only said that the coalition 
could put forward another candidate if there was a need for it. 

</TEXT>

