<H3> <TI>   Serb Army Deploys `Large Forces' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Serb Army Deploys `Large Forces' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU0804171194 Tirana TVSH Television Network in Albanian 1635 
GMT 8 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU0804171194 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana TVSH Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Albanian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Large Serbian Army forces, supplied with armored 
cars, tanks, and other military equipment, have been stationed 
in Hani i Elezit. These Serbian Army forces have also been 
deployed in Paldenice village near the Ramuka quarter. 
Transporters and other accompanying armaments have been placed 
in the trenches and are supplied with antiaircraft machine guns. 
  The Kosova Information Center reports that the Serbian 
soldiers and officers are performing military training and 
provoking the citizens of the area by raiding them. 

</TEXT>

