<H4>    Serbs Cite `Open Agression' </H4>

<F P=102> LD1004184394 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in 
Serbo-Croatian 1832 GMT 10 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1004184394 </F>
<F P=104>  Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service </F>
