  [Text] There was no peace in Gorazde overnight. The 
Chetniks attacked the southern access to the town (?with 
infantry) throughout the night. Until midnight, they were 
attacking individual parts of the town and the [word indistinct] 
itself with howitzer and tank grenades. Afterward, they 
attacked [words indistinct] defense lines with mortars and the 
town [word indistinct] with snipers. 
  This morning [words indistinct] somewhat intensified [words 
indistinct] that lasted here the entire night [words 
indistinct]. Shortly after 0800 [words indistinct], and infantry 
battles are under way in the area of the right bank access to 
the town. 
  According to preliminary reports, the consequences of the 
bestial overnight shelling are seven [words indistinct] and 
[word indistinct] injured. Some of them [passage indistinct] in 
